data.description: Welcome to the heart of downtown Blue Ridge! This stunningly renovated 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom home is the perfect blend of modern convenience and classic charm. From the moment you step inside, you'll be struck by the spacious & airy feel of this beautifully updated residence. The main house boasts an open-concept living area that's perfect for entertaining. The fully equipped kitchen features gleaming granite countertops, plenty of storage space and windows bringing in the natural light. The bedrooms are generously sized and offer ample closet space, while the bathrooms have been tastefully updated with thoughtful finishing touches. But that's not all - this property also features a separate basement apartment with a one bedroom, one bathroom layout. This space offers a separate entrance, making it the perfect option for a MIL suite or an income-producing rental. Whether you choose to use it for personal use or as an investment opportunity, the possibilities are endless! Don't miss your chance to make it yours today!
